                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/87090862/">Hobbit</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">越是看透人性的人，越是会温暖。感谢我的父母从小不加掩饰的让我直面人性，现在再看这本书倒也不惊讶，很理解。</p>
        </div>
